[[Tails_4.4.1|news/version_4.4.1]] fixes many security issues that affect
Tails 4.4. You should [[upgrade to Tails 4.4.1|news/version_4.4.1]] as
soon as possible.

 - Tor Browser: [9.0.7 release announcement](https://blog.torproject.org/new-release-tor-browser-907)
 - Tor: TROVE-2020-002 ([[!tor_bug 33120]], [[!cve CVE-2020-10592]]),
   TROVE-2020-003 ([[!tor_bug 33137]]), TROVE-2020-004 ([[!tor_bug 33619]], [[!cve CVE-2020-10593]])
 - Thunderbird: [[!mfsa 2020-10]], [[!debsa2020 4642]]
 - WebKitGTK: [[!debsa2020 4641]]
